389:          * is used prior to checking individual record retention. Only records from batches which were not
390:          * explicitly discarded with {@link BatchRetention#DELETE} will be considered.
391:          */
392:         protected abstract boolean shouldRetainRecord(RecordBatch recordBatch, Record record);
393:     }
